title: Pace Improvement Calculation
content:
Total 11km,  Speed control 6.5km/h - 8 km/h
If 5km, Speed control 8.5km/h - 9km/h
Pace make it under 8 km/h
Total time make it under 90 min, which is pace 8:11 km/h, which is  7.3 km/h speed min average
